content:
I dreamt I was a regular human in a giant sized world and they put objects that are familiar to humans in the world to trick them
I approached a dresser with a mirror and climbed up onto it and was quickly picked up by an evil looking being and decapitated by their teeth
And then when I died her reflection was in the mirror and the mirror shattered
And it turned into something similar to the playstation 5 screen that shows all of the squares
Like a bunch of glass squares and it loaded into a Google Play logo

what could this dream mean?
